{"type": "article", "id": 19329, "title": "12张铝片挂钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607111724S78dDXZCcOs4neNy.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏挂钟将 12 个小时用 12 张长方形铝片代替，没有具体的刻度，只有相邻之间的小的缺口来区别具体的时间。实际上它可以打开成任何的角度或重叠成其他形状挂在墙上，仅靠三根指针的方向来判断时间，以打破人们对时间的固有想法。它更方便之处在于可以收成一个长条形来运输。售价 40 美元起，有 8 种不同的配色。<a href=\"http://www.kibardindesign.com/e-shop/transformer-analog-black-black-clock-kibardin/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145837VDr6IYfwgAPJBR27.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145837uGXQtI8bjCTDzmfH.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145838lzKHgjfBZ5ipM8Eq.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145838srqJXF7QdLkRZHP3.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145839bSBwMC2U13VsAtgI.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"590\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}